subtitleNullable: Faces Data for Testing Facial Recognition
descriptionNullable:
This is a very small dataset consisting of faces of four of the following individuals:
- Elon Musk
- Jeff Bezos
- Mark Zuckerberg
- Bill Gates.

The training data contains a total of 60 images, 15 images for each of the individuals mentioned whereas the validation data contains 5 images for each of them totaling 20 images.
